              },
              "free_text": [
                " Metallic Ca-48 targets were",
                "prepared by evaporation from tungsten boats under",
                "vacuum, isotopically enriched in Ca-48 to 97.3%.",
                "Calcium metal 37.7 +- 1.4 mu-g/cm2 thick was evaporated",
                "and deposited onto a 0.25-mm tantalum substrate as",
                "well as a 0.25-mm crystalline silicon substrate.",
                "The target of 72.+- 8. mu-g/cm2 thick for the 48Ca",
                "on the Ta backing was used for the (p,gamma)",
                "measurements and both Ta-backed and Si-backed targets",
                "were used for (p,n) measurements."
              ]
            }
